Introduction

Cupid was a girl group under Narda Entertainment. They officially debuted on April 29, 2015, with the song "I Feel Good" under IN Entertainment, moving to Narda Entertainment in mid-2016. Cupid have also collaborated on singles with Rion Five and Chic Angel.
